                                Format Disk.


     If you have just bought some new  disks  then you will need to Format 
them by clicking once on  the  icon  and  Then  selecting  'Format'. If 
the disk has already been Formatted then you  can  use  Quick Format.

If the disk has hard errors then it's best to use Format.



